quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  95,1,I SWEAR by the FIG and by the olive
  95,2,By Mount Sinai
  95,3,And by this inviolate soil
  95,4,That of goodliest fabric we created man
  95,5,Then brought him down to be the lowest of the low
  95,6,"Save who believe and do the things that are right, for theirs shall be a reward that faileth not"
  95,7,"Then, who after this shall make thee treat the Judgment as a lie"
  95,8,What! is not God the most just of judges